---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import AmazonButton from '../../components/AmazonButton.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Sauna Reviews Backyard Sauna Pro"
  description="In-depth reviews of the best backyard saunas. Honest pros, cons, and verdicts on the most popular outdoor sauna kits."
  canonical="/reviews"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Sauna Reviews</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 mb-10">Honest reviews of the most popular backyard sauna kits real pros, cons, and verdicts.</p>

    <div class="mb-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm text-stone-600">
      <span class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Also see: </span>
      <a href="/reviews/harvia-kip-60b-review" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline font-medium mr-4">Harvia KIP 60B Electric Heater Review</a>
      <a href="/reviews/dynamic-saunas-barcelona-review" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline font-medium">Dynamic Saunas Barcelona Review</a>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">BEST OVERALL</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-3 mb-1">Almost Heaven Pinnacle 4-Person Barrel Sauna</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mb-3">Traditional Barrel · Cedar · 4-Person</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">The best-selling barrel sauna on Amazon and our overall top pick. Rustic red cedar construction, stainless steel hardware, and a barrel design that heats efficiently and sheds snow beautifully. Assembly takes 4–6 hours for two people and requires a 240V heater (sold separately).</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700 text-xs uppercase mb-1">What We Love</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Authentic Finnish sauna experience</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Barrel shape = excellent heat efficiency</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Cedar handles freeze-thaw cycles for decades</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Clean, beautiful aesthetic</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-red-600 text-xs uppercase mb-1">Watch Out For</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Heater not included budget $400–$600 extra</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Needs 240V dedicated circuit</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Takes up real yard space</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-3">Verdict: <span class="text-stone-600 font-normal">The best all-around choice for homeowners who want a real outdoor sauna experience. Buy it, install it well, and you'll use it for 20+ years.</span></p>
        <AmazonButton asin="B017WJV8SO" price="~$2,199" />
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">BEST BUDGET</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-3 mb-1">Dynamic Saunas Barcelona Far Infrared Sauna</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mb-3">Infrared · Canadian Hemlock · 1-2 Person</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">The best infrared sauna under $1,000. Low-EMF carbon panels, 15-minute heat-up time, plugs into a standard 120V outlet. No electrician needed, no special installation. If you want a real sauna experience without the complexity or cost of a traditional setup, this is the move.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700 text-xs uppercase mb-1">What We Love</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Plug-and-play no electrician</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Heats up in 15 minutes</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Low EMF certified panels</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Great for apartments, garages, spare rooms</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-red-600 text-xs uppercase mb-1">Watch Out For</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> 1-2 person only</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> No steam option</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Indoor/covered use only</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-3">Verdict: <span class="text-stone-600 font-normal">Best value in the sauna market. Not a traditional experience, but delivers real health benefits at a fraction of the cost and complexity.</span></p>
        <AmazonButton asin="B00A2F99F0" price="~$899" />
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">BEST LARGE</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-3 mb-1">Almost Heaven Saunas 6-Person Barrel Sauna</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mb-3">Traditional Barrel · Cedar · 6-Person</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">For families or those who want serious space, the 6-person barrel is the premium choice. Polished stainless steel hardware, clear-grade western Canadian red cedar, and enough room for two people to lie down comfortably. Built to outlast its owners.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-green-700 text-xs uppercase mb-1">What We Love</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Exceptional interior space</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Premium cedar and hardware quality</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Built for decades of use</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-red-600 text-xs uppercase mb-1">Watch Out For</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Significant yard space required</p>
            <p class="text-stone-600"> Higher price point</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-3">Verdict: <span class="text-stone-600 font-normal">If you're going to do it, do it right. The investment pays off in quality of experience and longevity.</span></p>
        <AmazonButton asin="B003Z11AXM" price="~$3,499" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
